properties.areaDesc: Whitefish Bay (U.S. Portion)/Whitefish Point to Point Iroquois MI
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 10 at 3:08PM EST until January 12 at 7:00AM EST by NWS Gaylord MI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Highest gusts up to 30 kt and highest waves around 7
feet expected.

* WHERE...Whitefish Bay (U. S. Portion)/Whitefish Point to Point
Iroquois MI.

* WHEN...From 10 PM this evening to 7 AM EST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 PM THIS EVENING TO 7 AM EST SUNDAY
